{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_120","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve pinned the remaining failures down to missing setter/constructor registrations for the stylesheet elements the tests actually use. `titles.xsl` needs `ElemApplyTemplates#setSelect(...)`, and `summary.xsl` needs `ElemParam#setSelect(...)`; `KeyDeclaration` is also a likely follow-on for the `xsl:key` path, so I’m adding that constructor now as well."}}
